## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on ethical hacking. Some sources may have inherent biases, and the rapidly evolving nature of cybersecurity means that new developments could alter the current understanding of ethical hacking's importance. Additionally, the lack of specific publication dates for some sources may affect the timeliness of the information.